plmxml_bus:SavedQueryDef.name: __ADMIN_Dispatcher_Requests
plmxml_bus:SavedQueryDef.Description: Search for all Dispatcher Request (Translation JT, ...)

plmxml_bus:QueryClause.stringValue: SELECT qid FROM DispatcherRequest WHERE "currentState" LIKE "${currentState = *}" AND "serviceName" = "${serviceName = }" AND "Dataset:primaryObjects.object_name" = "${DATASET:Name = }" AND "last_mod_user.user_id" = "${LastModifyingUser = }" AND "owning_user.user_id" = "${Owner = }" AND "priority" = "${priority = }" AND "creation_date" >= "${CreatedAfter = }" AND "creation_date" <= "${CreatedBefore = }" AND "lsd" >= "${ModifiedAfter = }" AND "last_mod_date" <= "${ModifiedBefore = }"
